Package gw.plugin.vendormanagement

Interface IServiceRequestLifecycle

All Superinterfaces:
InternalPlugin, Remote
public interface IServiceRequestLifecycle extends InternalPlugin
This plugin centralizes setup code for service requests and main related entities, allowing for core ClaimCenter features to leverage the ServiceRequest framework.

  • Method Details

    • createStateHandler

      ServiceRequestStateHandler createStateHandler(ServiceRequestKind kind)
      Creates a handler in the ServiceRequest lifecycle based on the kind of ServiceRequest which can be used for defining properties for operations in the ServiceRequest state machine.
      Parameters:
      kind - from Typelist ServiceRequestKind
      Returns:
      a type that extends abstract ServiceRequestStateHandler

    • initializeServiceRequest

      void initializeServiceRequest(ServiceRequest serviceRequest)
      Sets additional fields to the supplied serviceRequest. After serviceRequest is created, call this method to set additional fields.

      The out of box implementation of this method does nothing. Customers should implement this method to set any custom or additional values to the serviceRequest.

      Parameters:
      serviceRequest - ServiceRequest to set fields on

    • finishServiceRequestSetup

      void finishServiceRequestSetup(ServiceRequest serviceRequest, boolean isSpecialist)
      Completes setup of a Service Request before committing to database by ensuring necessary fields are set.
      Parameters:
      serviceRequest - the service request for which to finish setup
      isSpecialist - indicates if the promotion was done by the ServiceRequest specialist

    • initializeServiceRequestQuote

      void initializeServiceRequestQuote(ServiceRequestQuote quote, @Nullable ServiceRequestQuote baseSrQuote)
      Sets additional fields to quote, optionally using another quote as the base. If baseSrQuote is non-null, its fields are copied over to quote.
      Parameters:
      quote - the quote to set additional fields to
      baseSrQuote - a quote to copy fields from

    • finishQuoteSetup

      void finishQuoteSetup(ServiceRequestOperationContext context, boolean isSpecialist)
      Perform 'Add Quote' operation on quotes's service request
      Parameters:
      context - contains the parameters to perform the operation
      isSpecialist - if the operation is being performed by the specialist
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if ServiceRequestOperationContext.getStatement() is null, or is not of type ServiceRequestQuote

    • initializeServiceRequestInvoice

      void initializeServiceRequestInvoice(ServiceRequestInvoice serviceRequestInvoice)
      Sets additional fields on serviceRequestInvoice.
      Parameters:
      serviceRequestInvoice - the invoice to set additional fields to

    • finishInvoiceSetup

      void finishInvoiceSetup(ServiceRequestOperationContext context, boolean isSpecialist)
      Set invoice's status and perform 'Add Invoice' operation on invoice's service request
      Parameters:
      context - contains the parameters to perform the operation
      isSpecialist - if the operation is being performed by the specialist
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if ServiceRequestOperationContext.getStatement() is null, or is not of type ServiceRequestInvoice
